Estava na minha casa (EN)
Includes English Translation and Audio link

Iê na minha casa
Tava na minha casa
Sem pensar, sem imaginar
Mandaram me chamar
Pra ajudar a vencer
Mas a guerra do Paraná
Haha
Água de beber
Ei Aruandê
Aia quer me vender
Ie in my house
I was in my house
Without thinking, without imagining
They sent to call me
To help to beat
But it’s the war of  Paraná
Haha
Water to drink
Ei Aruandê
Aia wants to sell me

